### Full-text search
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search?q=machado

### Multi-word full-text
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search?q=memorias+postumas

### Full-text + area filter
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search?q=filosofia&area=Filosofia

### Area filter only (no query)
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search?area=Literatura+Brasileira

### Price filter + sort
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search?priceMax=5000&sort=price_asc

### State filter
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search?state=SP

### No results (fuzzy fallback)
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search?q=xyznonexistent

### No filters (list all)
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search

### Book detail with offers
GET http://localhost:8080/books/memorias-postumas-de-bras-cubas

### Academic areas
GET http://localhost:8080/books/academic-areas

### Active seller states
GET http://localhost:8080/sellers/active-states
